                                    <desc type="DonationNote">Donation note to the monastery of <ref type="ins" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS1018DabraE">Dabra ʾElgǝne</ref>.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">
                                        ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘወሀብዎ፡ ለደብረ፡ ኤልግኔ፡
                                    </q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus target="#86v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2807RepCh91">Malkǝʾ-hymn to Our Lady Mary</title>
                                        <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/X4SBAXAT"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Loefgren1974Katalog"/><title level="m">Katalog über die äthiopischen Handschriften in der Universitätsbibliothek Uppsala, Sowie Anhänge über äthiopische Handschriften in anderen Bibliotheken und in Privatbesitz in Schweden</title><title level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Oscar</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Löfgren</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Uppsala</pubPlace><publisher>Almqvist &amp; Wiksell</publisher><date>1974</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Acta Bibliothecae R. Universitatis Upsaliensis</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">18</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">18</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">39–40</citedRange></bibl>
                                        analyses this as two texts, one directed to Mary and another directed to Jesus. He reproduces the
                                        first stanza of the first part and the entire second part.
                                    </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"><seg part="I">
                                       <hi rend="rubric">ሰላም፡ ለኪ፡ ዘመ</hi>ዓዛ፡ አፉኪ፡ ኮል፡
                                        እንተ፡ ትጼንዊ፡ በገዳም፡ ወሐቅል፡
                                        ወልታ፡ ረዲኦትየ፡ በውስተ፡ ቀትል፡
                                    </seg></q>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"><seg part="F">
                                        <hi rend="rubric">ኢየሱስ፡ ሐመ፡</hi> ይቤ፡ በእንቲኣነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ሙቁሕ፡
                                        እንተ፡ አቀሙከ፡ ውስተ፡ አውደ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> 
                                        ፍ<supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ት</supplied>ሕ፡ 
                                        ጊዜ፡ ኮነ፡ ጎሐ፡ ጽባህ፡ ስብሐት። ለከ።
                                    </seg></q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <locus from="151va" to="152ra"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7065EsebbehSaggaki">ʾƎsebbǝḥ ṣaggāki</title>
                                    </desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"><seg part="I">
                                        እሴብ<supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ሕ</supplied>፡ <sic resp="JK">ጸጋክኪ፡</sic> 
                                        <sic resp="PRS6337Lofgren">ኦእግዚዕትየ፡</sic> ማርያም፡ 
                                        ታብር<del rend="effaced" unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ሒ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ልብየ፡ 
